title: TRAVELER CORP GIFT PACK - 12 UNITS
body_html:
Buy 12 Traveler umbrellas together and save 20% off the regular retail price. Umbrellas must be purchased together and discount does not apply if items are purchased separately.

Want to split up the 12 units with different colors? No problem! After you place your order, email us at support@davekny.com and specify the colors you'd like for the 12 units. Please include your Order Number with your request. All colors must be submitted no later than 10:00 am EST the next business day.

If you want to order more than 12 units, just enter a different quantity in the QTY field. A QTY of 2 will be 24 units, QTY 3 will be 36 units, etc. Orders must be in increments of 12 units.

All units individually packaged in elegant gift boxes.

title: THE DAVEK DUET - Larger size canopy for two
body_html:
Our extra-large weatherproof folded umbrella—big enough for two.

The DAVEK DUET is our extra-large foldable model—perfect for keeping two people dry. This extremely sturdy umbrella features a spacious canopy with a 55" coverage arc diameter, a high-quality genuine leather wrist strap, and sleek protective sleeve. The corrosion-resistant ribs offer both flexibility and durability.

Coverage: 55 in (arc-diam); 47 in (straight-diam)
Closed length: 14.75"
Weight: 1 lb 6 oz
Button system: Auto-open & auto-close
Frame: Extra large reinforced 8-rib frame system

title: THE DAVEK ELITE - Our classic cane umbrella
body_html:
Our modern take on the classic cane umbrella.

The DAVEK ELITE is our take on the classic cane umbrella. This handsome model is a perfect fit for both everyday use and formal occasions. Constructed with the absolute finest materials, the Davek Elite features a spacious 50" arc-diameter canopy and a soft, top-grain leather handle, elegantly stitched. Its flexible wind-tension frame system resists inversion in strong winds. The shaft is made of high-grade fiberglass for enhanced stability. A beautiful "waterfall" dome-shaped canopy is made of 210-thread count fabric, the tightest weave for umbrellas. The Davek Elite combines high-tech utility and classical elegance in a new and exciting way.

Coverage: 50 in (arc-diam); 44 in (straight-diam)
Closed length: 35"
Weight: 1 lb 9 oz
Button system: Auto-open system
Frame: Wind-tension fiberglass frame system

title: THE DAVEK GOLF - For the sports enthusiast
body_html:
Our largest umbrella for maximum coverage.

The DAVEK GOLF is our largest long-shafted umbrella, featuring a massive 62-inch arc diameter canopy. The Golf's exclusive "Duplex Frame" dual-canopy design navigates wind through its vented construction. The umbrella has been windtunnel-tested at MIT Aeronautics & Astronautics and guaranteed to endure gale-force winds of over 60 mph. An extremely strong fiberglass shaft gives the umbrella unsurpassed stability. Rotate the umbrella handle's base to expose a sleek aluminum-alloy "anchor spike". Push the spike into the turf to keep your open umbrella in place while taking your golf shot.

The Davek Golf is not only for golfers! It makes an ideal choice if you are looking for maximum coverage in any storm.

Coverage: 62 in (arc-diam); 55 in (straight-diam)
Closed length: 40"
Weight: 1 lb 15 oz
Button system: Auto-open system
Frame: Dual-canopy vented wind system
Extra feature: Reversible aluminum alloy anchor spike

title: THE DAVEK MINI - Our most compact
body_html:
A super compact umbrella—keep it with you always.

The DAVEK MINI is our smallest, most compact umbrella. This incredibly convenient umbrella fits in literally any compartment, from a handbag or clutch to your pants pocket. The stylish Mini is the perfect "just in case" umbrella, hardly noticeable when it's not in use. Keep it with you always—never be caught without an umbrella again. Measures less than 7 inches when closed. Pocket-sized protection, with style to spare.

Coverage: 38 in (arc-diam); 34 in (straight-diam)
Closed length: 7"
Weight: Under 1 lb—ultra-lightweight
Open/close system: Manual
Frame: Fiberglass reinforced 6-rib frame system

title: THE DAVEK SOLO - Our flagship umbrella
body_html:
The perfect individual-sized weatherproof umbrella.

With its sturdy frame construction and distinctive design, the DAVEK SOLO is the perfect combination of durability and sophisticated style. The umbrella features our unique wind resistant Davek RigidFlex™ Frame System and auto-open and auto-close button system. The waterproof canopy is constructed from the most tightly woven microweave fabric available. The gorgeous handle features a convenient clip to attach to your belt or hold in place within a bag. Elegant gift box included.

Coverage: 43 in (arc-diam); 37 in (straight-diam)
Closed length: 11.75"
Weight: 1 lb 2 oz
Button system: Auto-open & auto-close
Frame: Fiberglass reinforced 9-rib frame system

title: THE DAVEK TRAVELER - Small for easy portability
body_html:
Our small compact umbrella for easy travel.

The DAVEK TRAVELER is our compact travel model which features an extremely convenient, small frame system for easy portability. This model comes in an array of gorgeous colors and can easily fit in your bag or jacket pocket. Smaller and lighter than the Davek Solo and more robust than the Davek Mini, the Traveler is the perfect combination of convenience and durability. Comes with a soft, genuine leather wrist strap with a special clip to secure your umbrella to any bag strap.

Coverage: 40 in (arc-diam); 35 in (straight-diam)

title: THE DAVEK SAVILE - Our most exclusive
body_html:
Timeless elegance for the purist—our polished wood umbrella.

In the tradition of premium craftsmanship, the Davek Savile is handmade using traditional artisan techniques. The shaft and handle of this elegantly understated piece is hand-carved from a solid, continuous piece of natural chestnut wood, imported from Italy. Each Savile has the character and individuality of natural wood. No two are exactly the same. The Savile, quintessentially classic, has the unmatched sophistication of the Old World. The frame is composed of tempered steel, and the canopy of hand-cut, 190-thread count microweave fabric. A lifelong investment, the Savile is an heirloom that can be passed down from generation to generation. Hand-assembled in England.

Coverage: 55 in (arc-diam); 48 in (straight-diam)
Closed length: 37.5"
Weight: 1 lb 13 oz
Open/close system: Manual
Frame: Polished chestnut wood & tempered steel
